{"tid":1972260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急行動】427和你登記 DSE考場散場派選民登記表","createTime":"2020-04-14T11:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T06:00:03.000Z","uid":240968,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2de11d919385ed326e3c326d3b8a1f47a5471b8","tid":1972260,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"DSE就快開考<br />\n估計有約3萬考生今年7月25日滿18歲，<span style=\"color: gold;\">3萬票等於大半個議席</span>，絕對係登記最後衝刺既好機會!<br />\n呼籲3人<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(小心限聚令)</span></span>一隊抽時間去考場派選民登記表格<br />\n建議考完主科散場時喺門口派<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">四月二十七日</span></span></span>（星期一） 8:30 - 12:30通識教育<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">四月二十八日</span>（星期二）<br />\n8:30  - 13:00 英文<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">四月二十九日</span>（星期三） 9:15 - 12:10 英國語文 （三）（聆聽及綜合能力考核）<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">五月二日</span>（星期六） 8:30 - 12:45 數學<br />\n<br />\n詳細考試日期<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/mobile/tc/hkdse/admin/exam_timetable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fhkdse%2Fadmin%2Fexam_timetable%2F&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=7b013bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/mobile/tc/hkdse/admin/exam_timetable/</a><br />\n試場查詢<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2FHKDSE%2Fadmin%2Fexam_centres%2Fexam_centres.html&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=2b852afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html</a><br />\n<br />\n建議大家自行<br />\n印有QRcode單張<br />\n+<br />\n派選民登記表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=cf68033e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：<br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓"},{"pid":"d6ded60f7d0080627810ec6ae5b5652fa40ffaba","tid":1972260,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"推到區議員見到呢個post"},{"pid":"ac6928a8eda1e6ef9f7cdc8f5e9feaad8aac6221","tid":1972260,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:01:16.000Z","msg":"大把補習班 IVE 指南針打手幫你疲勞轟炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783f46aae64cbffaa598cb5463f660e0bc055dad","tid":1972260,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d28b23017029fc6ce1754a2b619555ccd3ad4a9e","tid":1972260,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17c41dd994006a6ab03fdd1b38a634c605f514ad","tid":1972260,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5e1c22122feba9534453599f1e56063a1ca6ba8","tid":1972260,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"推，一推再推"},{"pid":"63d0c329a138c12a1be2affbaa0afd78382295be","tid":1972260,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T03:30:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dcd671bd087bd4f06369c9a4ead2aac972993c5","tid":1972260,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3sgGXXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3sgGXXT.png&h=e9369ce6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0d9fd7b